opdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526275\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526275\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 06, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bwv1665702576896.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bwv1665702576896.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bwv1665702576896.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bwv1665702576896\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__validateocc_246753\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Validate an occurrence.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__topic_d79004e1_d79005e1_d79006e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__codeblock_rzh_dzy_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">validateocc  {Entity}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__section_w2580ab1b7b5_w2581ab1b7_w2582ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__p_d79010e1_d79011e1_d79012e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">validateocc \"CUSTOMER\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__topic_d51957e1_d51958e1_d51959e1_d51960e1_d51961e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d970040e74\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7724e1_d7725e1_d7726e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7724e1_d7725e1_d7726e1__entry__1\">Parameter </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7724e1_d7725e1_d7726e1__entry__2\"> DataType </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7724e1_d7725e1_d7726e1__entry__3\">Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7724e1_d7725e1_d7726e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7724e1_d7725e1_d7726e1__entry__2\">String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7724e1_d7725e1_d7726e1__entry__3\">Entity whose data is to be validated. If\n                        omitted, the current entity (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entname</span>) is used. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__topic_d51962e1_d51963e1_d51964e1_d51965e1_d51966e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d970040e130\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1__entry__1\">&lt;0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1__entry__2\">An error occurred.\n\t\t\t\t <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1__entry__1\">&gt;=0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bwv1665702576896__table_d7427e1_d7428e1_d7429e1__entry__2\">Statement executed successfully.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__topic_d51972e1_d51973e1_d51974e1_d51975e1_d51976e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d970040e189\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__d6417e20\">Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__topic_d51977e1_d51978e1_d51979e1_d51980e1_d51981e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d970040e198\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__p_d79037e1_d79038e1_d79039e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validateocc</span> statement validates\n            the current occurrence of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>. If any field of the occurrence is\n            marked as modified and has not been successfully validated, the necessary validation\n            triggers are activated. For more information, see the \"Validate\" topic.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__p_d79040e1_d79041e1_d79042e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validateocc</span> validates only the current occurrence; it does not\n            validate related inner entities. In contrast, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validate/o</span>\n            statement validates all inner entities in addition to the current occurrence.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__p_d79043e1_d79044e1_d79045e1\">You can use the function\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occvalidation</span> to determine if an occurrence requires\n            validation.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__p_d79046e1_d79047e1_d79048e1\">As each stage of the validation process completes\n            successfully, the corresponding validation flag (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldvalidation</span> and\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keyvalidation</span>) is set to 0. When the entire process completes\n            successfully, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occvalidation</span> is set to 0.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__note_w2583ab1b7c15c11_w2584ab1b7c15_w2585ab1b7_w2586ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Validation statements\n        (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validatefield</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validatekey</span>,\n        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validateocc</span>, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validate</span>) activate the validation\n      triggers such as validate and validatekey. You should therefore be careful when using these\n      statements in validation triggers.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__section_gjf_gzy_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d970040e256\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validateocc</span></h2>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104bwv1665702576896_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"bwv1665702576896__codeblock_hbn_hzy_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$MYOCC$ = \"CUSTOMER\"\nvalidateocc $MYOCC$</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrk1665702576500.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Validate</a><p>Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwi1665702576586.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatefield</a><p>Validate a field of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1665702576817.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatekey</a><p>Validate a key of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jnc1665702576977.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$entname</a><p>Return the name of the current entity or check for the existence of an entity in the component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jqe1665702576424.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$dataerrorcontext</a><p>Return the context of the last validation error.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/opq1665702649630.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$procerrorcontext</a><p>Return the location of the error specified by $procerror.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpz1719812992669.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occvalidation</a><p>Check whether an occurrence requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qdc1665702602510.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldvalidation</a><p>Identify whether a field requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wcw1719485700746.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keyvalidation</a><p>Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iwi1665702603846.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger validate (Entity)</a><p>System trigger for validating entity occurrences.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526275\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526275\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "validateocc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 06, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Validate an occurrence. validateocc {Entity} Copy Example: validateocc \"CUSTOMER\" Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter DataType Description Entity String Entity whose data is to be validated. If omitted, the current entity ( $entname ) is used. Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $status Value Meaning <0 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. >=0 Statement executed successfully. Use Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports. Description The validateocc statement validates the current occurrence of Entity . If any field of the occurrence is marked as modified and has not been successfully validated, the necessary validation triggers are activated. For more information, see the \"Validate\" topic. validateocc validates only the current occurrence; it does not validate related inner entities. In contrast, the validate/o statement validates all inner entities in addition to the current occurrence. You can use the function $occvalidation to determine if an occurrence requires validation. As each stage of the validation process completes successfully, the corresponding validation flag ( $fieldvalidation and $keyvalidation ) is set to 0. When the entire process completes successfully, $occvalidation is set to 0. Note: Validation statements ( validatefield , validatekey , validateocc , and validate ) activate the validation triggers such as validate and validatekey. You should therefore be careful when using these statements in validation triggers. Example: Using validateocc Explain this code $MYOCC$ = \"CUSTOMER\" validateocc $MYOCC$ Copy Related Links Validate Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default). validatefield Validate a field of the current occurrence. validatekey Validate a key of the current occurrence. $entname Return the name of the current entity or check for the existence of an entity in the component. $dataerrorcontext Return the context of the last validation error. $procerrorcontext Return the location of the error specified by $procerror. $occvalidation Check whether an occurrence requires validation. $fieldvalidation Identify whether a field requires validation. $keyvalidation Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation. trigger validate (Entity) System trigger for validating entity occurrences. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}